<dcterms:description xml:lang="en">This dataset consists of growth (length) data on Pike (Esox lucius) from net sampling in Windermere. Data collection began in 1944. The data were initially collected by the Freshwater Biological Association (FBA) but have been collected by CEH and its predecessor Institute of Freshwater Ecology (IFE) since 1989.</dcterms:description>     <dcterms:creator>clamw</dcterms:creator>     <dcterms:created rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime">2013-09-02T09:10:41Z</dcterms:created>   </documentcontainer:documentContainer> </rdf:RDF>
